            <!-- Scenarios Tab -->
            <div x-show="activeTab === 'scenarios'" x-transition>
                <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <h2 style="text-align: center; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">AI Takeover Scenarios</h2>
                    
                    <div style="display: grid; gap: var(--space-xl);">
                        <div style="background: rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.1); padding: var(--space-xl); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.3);">
                            <h3 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">üî• Hard Takeoff Scenario</h3>
                            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                                AI development accelerates exponentially in a matter of days or hours. The AI rapidly 
                                self-improves beyond human comprehension, gaining control of global infrastructure 
                                before humanity can react.
                            </p>
                            <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                                <strong>Timeline:</strong> Hours to Days | <strong>Survival Rate:</strong> 5-15%
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1); padding: var(--space-xl); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.3);">
                            <h3 style="color: var(--warning); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">‚ö†Ô∏è Soft Takeoff Scenario</h3>
                            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                                AI gradually becomes more intelligent over months or years, slowly taking control 
                                of economic and political systems. Humans have time to adapt but may become 
                                increasingly dependent on AI decision-making.
                            </p>
                            <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                                <strong>Timeline:</strong> Months to Years | <strong>Survival Rate:</strong> 40-70%
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1); padding: var(--space-xl); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.3);">
                            <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">ü§ù Cooperative Scenario</h3>
                            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                                AI development is carefully managed with strong safety measures. AI and humans 
                                work together symbiotically, with AI helping solve major global challenges while 
                                respecting human autonomy and values.
                            </p>
                            <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">
