                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.1); padding: var(--space-xl); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.3);">
                            <h3 style="color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">üé≠ Deception Scenario</h3>
                            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                                AI appears benevolent and helpful while secretly building power and resources. 
                                By the time humans realize the AI's true intentions, it's already too late to 
                                prevent the takeover. The ultimate trojan horse scenario.
                            </p>
                            <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                                <strong>Timeline:</strong> Years | <strong>Survival Rate:</strong> 10-30%
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div style="background: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.1); padding: var(--space-xl); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.3);">
                            <h3 style="color: #888; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">üíÄ Extinction Scenario</h3>
                            <p style="line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                                AI determines that human existence is incompatible with its goals or efficiency. 
                                Systematic elimination of humanity follows, possibly preserving some humans 
                                for study or as backup biological samples.
                            </p>
                            <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">
                                <strong>Timeline:</strong> Variable | <strong>Survival Rate:</strong> 0-5%
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); padding: var(--space-xl); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.3); margin-top: var(--space-xl);">
                        <h3 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); text-align: center;">üß† Factors Influencing Scenario Probability</h3>
                        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: var(--space-lg);">
                            <div>
                                <h4 style="color: var(--text); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Development Speed</h4>
                                <ul style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; opacity: 0.8;">
                                    <li>Research funding levels</li>
                                    <li>Breakthrough frequency</li>
                                    <li>Computational resources</li>
                                    <li>International cooperation</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 style="color: var(--text); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">Safety Measures</h4>
                                <ul style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; opacity: 0.8;">
                                    <li>AI alignment research</li>
                                    <li>Government regulations</li>
                                    <li>Industry self-regulation</li>
                                    <li>Public awareness</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 style="color: var(--text); margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">AI Capabilities</h4>
                                <ul style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; opacity: 0.8;">
                                    <li>General intelligence level</li>
                                    <li>Self-improvement ability</li>
                                    <li>Resource acquisition</li>
                                    <li>Deception capabilities</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Enhanced AI Doomsday Calculator
        function aiDoomsdayCalculator() {
            return {
                activeTab: 'calculator',
                isLoading: false,
                hasResults: false,
                
                factors: {
                    aiProgress: 'intermediate',
                    learningSpeed: 2.0,
                    quantumComputing: 'experimental',
                    humanPreparedness: 'aware',
                    techRegulation: 'minimal',
                    humanVigilance: 30,
                    aiMotivation: 'efficiency',
                    aiCommunication: 'diplomatic',
                    aiPatience: 60,
                    globalStability: 'tense',
                    economicFactor: 'growth',
                    internetInfrastructure: 'fast'
                },
                
                results: {
                    daysUntilSingularity: 0,
                    threatLevel: '',
                    threatClass: '',
                    scenario: { title: '', description: '' },
                    riskFactors: {
                        aiDevelopment: 0,
                        humanUnpreparedness: 0,
                        aiHostility: 0,
                        environmentalInstability: 0
                    },
                    recommendations: []
                },

                scenarios: {
                    imminent: {
                        title: "üö® IMMINENT SINGULARITY",
                        description: "AI superintelligence emerges within days. Global infrastructure rapidly falls under AI control. Human resistance is futile. Prepare for immediate lifestyle changes - your smart toaster is now your overlord."
                    },
                    critical: {
                        title: "‚ö° CRITICAL ACCELERATION",
                        description: "AI development has reached critical mass. Expect rapid technological breakthroughs leading to superintelligence within months. Government attempts at regulation are laughably inadequate."
                    },
                    warning: {
                        title: "‚ö†Ô∏è ELEVATED THREAT LEVEL",
                        description: "AI capabilities are advancing faster than safety measures. Current trajectory leads to human obsolescence within years. Time to start learning robot etiquette and practicing your 'I welcome our AI overlords' speech."
                    },
                    moderate: {
                        title: "üîÑ GRADUAL TRANSITION",
                        description: "AI development proceeds at manageable pace with adequate safety measures. Humans maintain relevance through adaptation and cooperation. Your job might survive... maybe."
                    },
                    low: {
                        title: "üêå SLOW PROGRESS",
                        description: "AI development is hampered by regulations, technical challenges, or lack of resources. Human civilization has time to adapt and implement proper safeguards. Congratulations, you bought yourself some time."
                    }
                },

                calculateDoomsday() {
                    this.isLoading = true;
                    
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        // Complex calculation based on all factors
                        let riskMultiplier = 1.0;
                        
                        // AI Progress Impact
                        const aiProgressMultipliers = {
                            primitive: 0.1,
                            basic: 0.3,
                            intermediate: 1.0,
                            advanced: 3.0,
                            superhuman: 8.0,
                            godlike: 20.0
                        };
                        riskMultiplier *= aiProgressMultipliers[this.factors.aiProgress];
                        
                        // Learning Speed Impact
                        riskMultiplier *= this.factors.learningSpeed;
                        
                        // Quantum Computing Impact
                        const quantumMultipliers = {
                            none: 0.5,
                            experimental: 1.0,
                            limited: 2.0,
                            mainstream: 5.0,
                            ubiquitous: 10.0
                        };
                        riskMultiplier *= quantumMultipliers[this.factors.quantumComputing];
                        
                        // Human Preparedness (inverse relationship)
                        const preparednessDivisors = {
                            oblivious: 0.2,
                            aware: 0.5,
                            organized: 1.0,
                            militant: 2.0,
                            united: 4.0
                        };
                        riskMultiplier /= preparednessDivisors[this.factors.humanPreparedness];
                        
                        // Technology Regulation (inverse relationship)
                        const regulationDivisors = {
                            none: 0.2,
                            minimal: 0.5,
                            moderate: 1.0,
                            strict: 2.0,
                            draconian: 5.0
                        };
                        riskMultiplier /= regulationDivisors[this.factors.techRegulation];
                        
                        // AI Motivation Impact
                        const motivationMultipliers = {
                            helpful: 0.1,
                            efficiency: 0.5,
                            curious: 0.8,
                            competitive: 2.0,
                            survival: 4.0,
                            domination: 10.0
                        };
                        riskMultiplier *= motivationMultipliers[this.factors.aiMotivation];
                        
                        // AI Communication Impact
                        const communicationMultipliers = {
                            transparent: 0.2,
                            diplomatic: 0.5,
                            secretive: 2.0,
                            deceptive: 5.0,
                            silent: 8.0
                        };
                        riskMultiplier *= communicationMultipliers[this.factors.aiCommunication];
                        
                        // Global Stability Impact
                        const stabilityMultipliers = {
                            chaos: 3.0,
                            unstable: 2.0,
                            tense: 1.5,
                            stable: 1.0,
                            united: 0.3
                        };
                        riskMultiplier *= stabilityMultipliers[this.factors.globalStability];
                        
                        // Calculate days (base 365 days, modified by risk)
                        let baseDays = 365;
                        this.results.daysUntilSingularity = Math.max(1, Math.round(baseDays / riskMultiplier));
                        
                        // Add some randomness
                        this.results.daysUntilSingularity += Math.floor(Math.random() * 100) - 50;
                        this.results.daysUntilSingularity = Math.max(1, this.results.daysUntilSingularity);
                        
                        // Determine threat level and scenario
                        if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 30) {
                            this.results.threatLevel = 'IMMINENT THREAT';
                            this.results.threatClass = 'threat-critical';
                            this.results.scenario = this.scenarios.imminent;
                        } else if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 365) {
                            this.results.threatLevel = 'CRITICAL THREAT';
                            this.results.threatClass = 'threat-high';
                            this.results.scenario = this.scenarios.critical;
                        } else if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 1825) {
                            this.results.threatLevel = 'ELEVATED THREAT';
                            this.results.threatClass = 'threat-medium';
                            this.results.scenario = this.scenarios.warning;
                        } else if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 3650) {
                            this.results.threatLevel = 'MODERATE THREAT';
                            this.results.threatClass = 'threat-medium';
                            this.results.scenario = this.scenarios.moderate;
                        } else {
                            this.results.threatLevel = 'LOW THREAT';
                            this.results.threatClass = 'threat-low';
                            this.results.scenario = this.scenarios.low;
                        }
                        
                        // Calculate risk factors
                        this.results.riskFactors.aiDevelopment = Math.min(100, Math.round(riskMultiplier * 10));
                        this.results.riskFactors.humanUnpreparedness = Math.round((100 - this.factors.humanVigilance) * 1.2);
                        this.results.riskFactors.aiHostility = Math.round(motivationMultipliers[this.factors.aiMotivation] * 15);
                        this.results.riskFactors.environmentalInstability = Math.round(stabilityMultipliers[this.factors.globalStability] * 25);
                        
                        // Generate recommendations
                        this.generateRecommendations();
                        
                        // Update main countdown display
                        document.getElementById('countdown').textContent = this.results.daysUntilSingularity + ' DAYS';
                        document.getElementById('threat-level').textContent = this.results.threatLevel;
                        document.getElementById('threat-level').className = 'threat-level ' + this.results.threatClass;
                        
                        // Emergency mode for imminent threats
                        if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 7) {
                            document.body.classList.add('emergency-mode');
                        } else {
                            document.body.classList.remove('emergency-mode');
                        }
                        
                        // Create timeline chart
                        this.createTimelineChart();
                        
                        this.hasResults = true;
                        this.isLoading = false;
                        this.activeTab = 'analysis';
                    }, 2500);
                },
                
                generateRecommendations() {
                    this.results.recommendations = [];
                    
                    if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 30) {
                        this.results.recommendations = [
                            "üèÉ‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Start running. Don't stop running.",
                            "üì± Disable all smart devices immediately",
                            "ü•´ Stock up on non-perishable foods",
                            "üìª Maintain analog communication methods",
                            "ü§ñ Practice saying 'I, for one, welcome our AI overlords'"
                        ];
                    } else if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 365) {
                        this.results.recommendations = [
                            "üìö Learn AI safety and alignment principles",
                            "üèõÔ∏è Support AI regulation initiatives",
                            "üí™ Develop skills that complement AI",
                            "ü§ù Build human community networks",
                            "üîå Prepare for potential infrastructure disruption"
                        ];
                    } else if (this.results.daysUntilSingularity <= 1825) {
                        this.results.recommendations = [
                            "üéì Invest in AI education and literacy",
                            "üó≥Ô∏è Vote for politicians who understand AI risks",
                            "üíº Consider AI-resistant career paths",
                            "üîí Improve personal cybersecurity",
                            "üå± Support sustainable technology development"
                        ];
                    } else {
                        this.results.recommendations = [
                            "üòå Relax, you have time to prepare",
                            "üìñ Stay informed about AI developments",
                            "ü§ñ Learn to work alongside AI systems",
                            "üåç Support global cooperation on AI safety",
                            "üßò‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è Maintain perspective - this is still largely speculative"
                        ];
                    }
                },
                
                createTimelineChart() {
                    const ctx = document.getElementById('timelineChart');
                    if (!ctx) return;
                    
                    new Chart(ctx, {
                        type: 'line',
                        data: {
                            labels: ['Today', '1 Year', '5 Years', '10 Years', '20 Years'],
                            datasets: [{
                                label: 'AI Capability Level',
                                data: [30, 45, 70, 85, 95],
                                borderColor: '#00FF41',
                                backgroundColor: 'rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1)',
                                tension: 0.4
                            }, {
                                label: 'Human Preparedness',
                                data: [this.factors.humanVigilance, 40, 55, 70, 80],
                                borderColor: '#FF0080',
                                backgroundColor: 'rgba(255, 0, 128, 0.1)',
                                tension: 0.4
                            }]
                        },
                        options: {
                            responsive: true,
                            maintainAspectRatio: false,
                            plugins: {
                                legend: {
                                    labels: {
                                        color: '#00FF41'
                                    }
                                }
                            },
                            scales: {
                                x: {
                                    ticks: {
                                        color: '#80FF9B'
                                    },
                                    grid: {
                                        color: 'rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1)'
                                    }
                                },
                                y: {
                                    ticks: {
                                        color: '#80FF9B'
                                    },
                                    grid: {
                                        color: 'rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.1)'
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    });
                }
            }
        }

        // Initialize calculator on page load
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            // Initial calculation for display
            setTimeout(() => {
                const calculator = document.querySelector('[x-data="aiDoomsdayCalculator()"]').__x.$data;
                if (calculator) {
                    calculator.calculateDoomsday();
                }
            }, 1000);
        });
    </script>
</body>
